<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Welcome to Switchgate (Client)</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; background: #f9fafb; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; padding: 24px; }
    .brand { font-weight: 700; color: #01796F; }
    .card { background: #e6f2f0; border: 1px solid #01796F; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; }
    .credentials { font-family: monospace; background: #f1f5f9; padding: 12px; border-radius: 6px; }
    .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 24px; }
    a { color: #01796F; text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="brand">Switchgate</div>

    <h2>Welcome, {{clientName}}!</h2>

    <p>Your organization account has been successfully created on Switchgate.</p>

    <div class="card">
      <p><strong>Here are your credentials:</strong></p>
      <div class="credentials">
        <p>Client ID: {{clientId}}</p>
        <p>Client Secret: {{clientSecret}}</p>
        <p>API Key: {{apiKey}}</p>
      </div>
      <p>Please keep these credentials secure. They are required to authenticate your applications with Switchgate.</p>
    </div>

    <p>If you did not request this account, please contact our support team immediately at
      <a href="mailto:support@switchgate.com">support@switchgate.com</a> or <a href="tel:09031682798">09031682798</a>.
    </p>

    <p>Kind Regards,<br />Switchgate Team</p>

    <div class="footer">
      Youâ€™re receiving this because a client account was created for your organization.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>